# 🏡 Elder Echoes – UX Case Study  

🔗 [**Live Figma Prototype**](https://www.figma.com/design/hSH00Gp0KRB3vPVCkYSwEy/Elder-Echoes-Case-Study?node-id=0-1&p=f&t=YsKHNTM5nuzMc8C4-0)  
📄 [**Full Case Study Report**](https://www.notion.so/Connect-the-elderly-to-beat-their-loneliness-and-them-stay-healthy-cf6d4ec369bb4640aa36951036919c9c?pvs=4)  


## 🔍 Overview  
Elder Echoes is a mobile app designed to combat senior loneliness through digital storytelling and interactive events.  

## 📊 Research & Insights  
- Identified digital adoption challenges among seniors  
- Conducted competitive analysis vs. Stitch, Facebook Groups  
- Created **personas & journey maps** for targeted feature development  

## 🎨 UX Process  
1️⃣ **Wireframing & Prototyping** – Senior-friendly UI in Figma  
2️⃣ **Usability Testing** – A/B testing led to 30% smoother navigation  
3️⃣ **Final Iterations** – Added sidebar navigation + onboarding flow  

## 🛠 Tools Used  
- Figma (Design & Prototyping)  
- Maze (Usability Testing)  
- Miro (Affinity Mapping)  

